<paragraph pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Distinguishing features.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Leaves lanceolate or oblong, at least 2 cm wide. Inflorescence usually of several flowers.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
